text: Ringoes is an unincorporated community and census-designated place located within East Amwell Township in Hunterdon County, New Jersey, United States.State of New Jersey Census Designated Places - BVP20 - Data as of January 1, 2020, United States Census Bureau. Accessed December 1, 2022. 849 people lived here in 2020. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in New Jersey Category:Hunterdon County, New Jersey
